---
import { site } from "@/data/site";
import { withBase } from "@/lib/path";
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-brand-navy" data-vision-hero>
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img class="h-full w-full object-cover object-center" src={withBase("/images/studio/studio-iheal-lineup-hero.jpg")} alt="iHEAL 대표 제품 스튜디오 이미지" />
    <div class="absolute inset-y-0 left-0 w-[min(980px,86vw)] bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-navy/90 via-brand-navy/64 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="container-page relative flex min-h-[620px] items-center py-20 text-white lg:min-h-[700px]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <p class="mb-6 text-sm font-black tracking-[0.34em] text-emerald-200">VISION OF BIOLAB</p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-black leading-[1.25] sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        건강의 내일은<br class="hidden sm:block" />
        오늘의 작은 기준에서 시작됩니다
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-8 max-w-2xl text-lg font-semibold leading-8 text-slate-100">
        비오랩은 원료를 고르는 기준, 제품을 설계하는 태도, 고객에게 전달되는 경험까지 건강한 일상의 기준을 세웁니다.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-12 grid max-w-3xl gap-px overflow-hidden bg-white/25 text-sm font-bold text-white sm:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="bg-brand-navy/55 px-5 py-4 backdrop-blur-sm">Functional Ingredients</div>
        <div class="bg-brand-navy/55 px-5 py-4 backdrop-blur-sm">Women & Kids Health</div>
        <div class="bg-brand-navy/55 px-5 py-4 backdrop-blur-sm">Global Brand Channels</div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-8 text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.24em] text-emerald-100">{site.englishName}</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
